node.text:
His heart was full of love, he was dangerous, he was a guardian, he was always happy to see us and he was one of the few dogs that actually smiled to show us he loved us.
.
I tried really hard to bring him back. I’m gonna miss that smile. Might need a minute. 
.
Thank you to everyone whom showed Rambo love over the years. He loved you back. 
.
No matter what challenges you face, keep going. Take a minute to process, and then put one foot in front of the other knowing how strong you’ll be on the other side of it. 
.
Tough few days for me. Better days ahead. Continuing the journey. 
.
Seriously, everyone that showed him love. Thank you. It meant the world to him. 
.
Stay strong. 🙏🏻
